data.title: Premier Episode Of "DJs Love Beer" Web Series, Feat. DJ Jazzy Joyce
data.meta_description: The web series "DJs Love Beer" was created to give people more insight on the lives of DJs and introduce people to the world of craft beer, both being things I am very fond of. Season 1 is in the bag and now we need viewers to watch and share with all of their DJ loving, beer drinking friends! Your
